## 配置和扩展

### 自定义规则
支持添加团队特定的编码规则：
```yaml
custom_rules:
  - id: xp_custom_naming
    name: "小鹏自定义命名规范"
    pattern: "^XP[A-Z][a-zA-Z0-9]*$"
    severity: error
    file_patterns: ["**/*.h"]
```

### 权限矩阵配置
灵活配置不同角色的权限：
```yaml
roles:
  senior_architect:
    permissions:
      - "vehicle_sdk:write"
      - "ai_assist:all_modules"
  vehicle_team_member:
    permissions:
      - "vehicle_sdk:read"
      - "vehicle_sdk:write"
  business_developer:
    permissions:
      - "business_modules:read"
      - "business_modules:write"
```

